Maze.capacity1.desc:
warning - Only one more block may be added. Please include '%1' in the translated string. It will be replaced with '1' and made bold.

See also:
* {{msg-blockly|Maze.capacity2}}

Maze.capacity2.desc:
warning - Only %2 more blocks may be used, where %2 is an integer greater than 1.

See also:
* {{msg-blockly|Maze.capacity1}}

Bird.helpElseIf.desc:
callout - This is shown when the user first needs to modify an 'if' block to have an 'else if' and an 'else'.

Make sure to translate consistently with:
* {{msg-blockly|CONTROLS IF MSG ELSEIF}}
* {{msg-blockly|CONTROLS IF MSG ELSE}}

Bird.helpAnd.desc:
callout - This is shown to introduce the user to the logical 'and' block.

Make sure to translate consistently with:
* {{msg-blockly|LOGIC OPERATION AND}}

Bird.helpMutator.desc:
callout - This is shown to demonstrate how to drag a block.

Translate consistently with:
* {{msg-blockly|CONTROLS IF MSG ELSE}}
* {{msg-blockly|CONTROLS IF MSG IF}}

